<p>Dave and John kick off this week&rsquo;s show with a <em>healthy</em>&nbsp;dose of Cool Stuff Found. Then it&rsquo;s time for a little discussion about the future of <em>Mac Geek Gab Premium</em>&nbsp;(and what a future it will be!). Following that are answers to your questions &hellip; lots of &lsquo;em, too. Download today (the show&rsquo;s free to listen to!) and enjoy.</p>
